        <mxCell id="bottleneck" value="BOTTLENECK: 180 s/shovel vs. 15.84 s takt (LOCKED) &#8594; ceil(180/15.84) = 12 parallel stations needed (8 sharpen + 4 serrate) — by far the largest footprint/labour requirement in the process. See report Section 7 capacity logic — do not hide this in an appendix." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#990000;" vertex="1" parent="1">
