        <mxCell id="caption" value="Figure — Station 8: Sharpening + Serrating. THIS IS THE PROCESS BOTTLENECK. Sharpen 2 min + serrate 1 min = 180 s/shovel (LOCKED) vs. takt 15.84 s/shovel (LOCKED): parallel stations needed = ceil(180/15.84) = 12 (8 sharpen + 4 serrate, split by sub-operation). No scrap adjustment — downstream of the sheet-stamping scrap point. Compare against alternative block layouts before finalising floor area here." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
